sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant Server as Server
    participant Recipient1 as Recipient 1
    participant Recipient2 as Recipient 2
    participant Group as Group

    User->>Server: Send Message
    Server-->>User: Acknowledge Message Sent
    Server->>Group: Deliver Message to Recipients
    Group->>Recipient1: Deliver Message
    Group->>Recipient2: Deliver Message
    Group-->>Server: Acknowledge Message Delivered

    Recipient1->>Group: Read Message
    Recipient2->>Group: Read Message
    Group-->>Server: Update Read Status for Recipients
    Server-->>User: Notify Read Receipts